<doc id="201662" wikidata="Q1727077" url="?curid=201662" title="Patkul">
<text>Patkul may refer to:

* Johann Patkul, Livonian politician and agitator of Baltic German extraction
* German exonym for Patkule, a village in Latvia</text><links>
